The,VivaPayments,service,allows,online,store,owners,to,accept,payments,sent,via,email,phone,e,banking,or,a,physical,location,VivaPayments,also,provides,next,day,deposits,interest,free,monthly,installments,and,support,for,tax,card,transactions,The,VivaPayments,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,service,with,their,e,commerce,websites,via,REST,calls,The,three,functions,that,must,be,integrated,for,VivaPayments,to,work,are,the,abilities,to,create,payment,orders,complete,payment,details,and,confirm,transactions